    <user>dimstar_suse</user>
    <comment>- update to 0.5.8:
  * Fix for not connecting after sleep/wake
  * Fix boot loop and improve suspend/resume reconnection
  * dongle: fix beacon loopback and duplicate WCID allocation</comment>
